Package: circumflex
Version: __VERSION__
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: __ARCH__
Maintainer: circumflex maintainers <opensource@local.invalid>
Homepage: https://github.com/bensadeh/circumflex
Depends: libc6
Description: Command line tool for browsing Hacker News in your terminal
 circumflex is a terminal application for browsing Hacker News,
 reading comment threads, and opening articles in a reader-friendly view.
 This package installs the clx binary and man page.
